        {
            "title": "彭博 : 港元今日曾觸及弱方兌換保證",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">《彭博》報道，港元兌美元今日一度觸及弱方兌換保證，跌至7.85水平，為2023年以來首次。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20250225-162156_2025預算案_財政儲備_財政_政府收入_財赤_港元_source-licensed__704px.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20250225-162156_2025預算案_財政儲備_財政_政府收入_財赤_港元_source-licensed__704px.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">報道稱，港息低企，融資成本低，導至投資者借港元買入美元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">《彭博》稱，港元兌美元自5月高位至今下跌超過1%，為自1983年聯匯制度以來最大單月跌幅。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金管局周四稱，若港元觸及弱方兌換保證，將觸發金管局按聯匯制度買入港元沽出美元，銀行結餘將下降，港元拆息將上升。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15026471-%e5%bd%ad%e5%8d%9a-%e6%b8%af%e5%85%83%e4%bb%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%9b%be%e8%a7%b8%e5%8f%8a%e5%bc%b1%e6%96%b9%e5%85%8c%e6%8f%9b%e4%bf%9d%e8%ad%89",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/bplib_20230707-125253_20230707_FI_source-licensed_HKD_shutterstock_fb_1_source-licensed_.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-20 16:25:56",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "內地香港跨境支付星期日上線",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國人民銀行宣布，內地與香港快速支付系統互聯互通(簡稱跨境支付通)將於本月22日上線運行。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"人行行長潘功勝。圖片來源 : 人民銀行網站\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/800x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250620_FI_PBOC_HKMA_payment-connect_800_1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"人行行長潘功勝。圖片來源 : 人民銀行網站\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/800x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250620_FI_PBOC_HKMA_payment-connect_800_1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">人行行長潘功勝。圖片來源 : 人民銀行網站</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">跨境人民銀行與香港金管局早上聯合舉辦跨境支付通啟動儀式。人行表示，通過內地網上支付跨行清算系統與香港快速支付系統「轉數快」直接連接，支持參與機構為兩地居民提供跨境支付服務。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">下一步，人民銀行將與香港金管局加強監管合作，保障跨境支付通平穩有序運行。會同兩地快速支付系統運營機構和各參與機構，進一步完善相關制度安排。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"金管局主席余偉文。圖片來源: 人民銀行網站\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/800x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250620_FI_PBOC_HKMA_payment-connect_800.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"金管局主席余偉文。圖片來源: 人民銀行網站\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/800x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250620_FI_PBOC_HKMA_payment-connect_800.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">金管局主席余偉文。圖片來源: 人民銀行網站</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15026424-%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e8%b7%a8%e5%a2%83%e6%94%af%e4%bb%98%e6%98%9f%e6%9c%9f%e6%97%a5%e4%b8%8a%e7%b7%9a",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250620_FI_PBOC_HKMA_payment-connect_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-20 16:15:29",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "聯邦制藥收取諾和諾德1.8億美元預付款",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">聯邦制藥(03933)公布，已收取丹麥諾和諾德的預付款1.8億美元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"聯邦制藥中期報告\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/764x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250325_FI_03933_.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"聯邦制藥中期報告\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/764x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250325_FI_03933_.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">聯邦制藥中期報告</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">公司今年3月公布，與丹麥諾和諾德訂立獨家許可協議，共同開發治療肥胖、2型糖尿病和其他疾病藥物「UBT251」。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">按相關協議，聯邦制藥若達成指定開發和銷售里程碑，將有資格進一步收取最高18億美元的潛在里程碑付款，以及可收取基於該地區的年度淨銷售額計算的分層銷售提升。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15026361-%e8%81%af%e9%82%a6%e5%88%b6%e8%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%8f%96%e8%ab%be%e5%92%8c%e8%ab%be%e5%be%b71-8%e5%84%84%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%e9%a0%90%e4%bb%98%e6%ac%be",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250407_FI_source-web_03933-1-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-20 15:51:02",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "A股收跌   深股曾破萬點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股收跌，深股一度跌破萬點關，一周累計滬股跌0.5%，深股跌逾1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20190507_FI_A股_FB-1-2-3-1-5_source-ap_-2-1-1-3.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20190507_FI_A股_FB-1-2-3-1-5_source-ap_-2-1-1-3.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指收跌2點或0.07%，報3359點，今早開報3358點，跌4點或0.12%，早段高見3370點，升8點或0.24%，為全日高位，全日最低見3357點，跌5點或0.15%，成交4108.73億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">一周計累跌17點或0.5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指收跌46點或0.47%，報10005點，今早開報10039，跌12點或0.12%，最高見10084，升33點或0.33%，其後反覆向下，臨近收市跌破萬點，報9998點，跌53點或0.53%，為全日低位。全日成交6568.13億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">一周計累跌117點或1.16%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300收升3點或0.09%，報3846點，創業板指數收跌16點或0.83%，報2009點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15026276-a%e8%82%a1%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c-%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e6%9b%be%e7%a0%b4%e8%90%ac%e9%bb%9e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097537633130-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-20 15:30:31",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "荃灣萬景峰522實呎戶840萬易手 原業主持貨10年賺60萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15021064&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美聯物業海濱花園分行最新促成荃灣萬景峰522實呎戶，以840萬元易手。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">成交單位為荃灣萬景峰6座中層G室，實用面積522平方呎，原業主3月時以1080萬元放售，至月初因應市況下調叫價至880萬元，而新買家為同區租客，轉租為買，經過數次協商，單位最終以840萬成交，實用呎價約16091元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">原業主於2015年以780萬元購入單位，一直作長線收租之用，是次轉手，帳面獲利60萬元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15021064-%e8%8d%83%e7%81%a3%e8%90%ac%e6%99%af%e5%b3%b0522%e5%af%a6%e5%91%8e%e6%88%b6840%e8%90%ac%e6%98%93%e6%89%8b-%e5%8e%9f%e6%a5%ad%e4%b8%bb%e6%8c%81%e8%b2%a810%e5%b9%b4%e8%b3%ba60%e8%90%ac",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-20 15:10:37",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "將軍澳蔚藍灣畔2房戶708萬成交   持貨4年蝕142萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15021038&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">利嘉閣地產將軍澳蔚藍灣畔二行促成將軍澳蔚藍灣畔6座中層A室的二手成交個案，單位實用面積約506方呎，屬2房間隔，遠望山景。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該行稱，新買家為區內換樓客，業主原叫價760萬元，議價至708萬元成交，折合實用面積呎價約13,992元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">據悉，原業主於2021年以約850萬元買入單位。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該屋苑現有約79個單位放盤，最低入場費由約680萬元起。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15021038-%e5%b0%87%e8%bb%8d%e6%be%b3%e8%94%9a%e8%97%8d%e7%81%a3%e7%95%942%e6%88%bf%e6%88%b6708%e8%90%ac%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4-%e6%8c%81%e8%b2%a84%e5%b9%b4%e8%9d%95142%e8%90%ac",
